title: 820-2838 Green led no boot
message:
Hi
this board liquid near U7000 & U7201, i change the caps damage.
I have green led
G3 rails are good, S5 rail too, but S3 rails are 0V except PP5V_S3_REG, and S0 rail at 0V
SMC_PM_G2_EN=3,433V
PM_SLP_S4_L=0V
PM_SLP_S3_L=0V
Y2810  pin1 =1,569 . pin2=1,750V
I try to short the power pad but nothing, i have SMC_ONOF_L = 3,433V

title: 820-2838 Green led no boot
message: PP5V_S3_REG cannot be present if PM_SLP_S4_L=0V. Go back and check again. You must manually power on these boards.

title: 820-2838 Green led no boot
message: PP5V_S3_REG=0 indeed. when i short power pad (R5015), the fan do nothing and the power rail S3 and S0, always to 0v.

title: 820-2838 Green led no boot
message: U7201 already replaced? It could be so many things. Inspect corroded areas again. Crap under SMC/MCP maybe?
